Titolo: Pyre (video game)

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Pyre is a 2017 action role-playing video game developed and published by Supergiant Games. It was released in July 2017 for Microsoft Windows, Linux and PlayStation 4, and in August 2017 for macOS. Elements from  sports games were incorporated to the title's gameplay. It was the third game developed by Supergiant following Transistor (2014) and it received generally positive reviews upon release.

Genere: Action role-playing 

Valutazione: N/A
